"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1105297","Ministry of Housing, Communities and Local Government","false","2019-04-01","<p>I refer the Hon Member to my answer of 22 February 2019 to Question UIN 220837.</p>","North West Hampshire","Kit Malthouse",,"2019-04-01T14:09:19.65Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1105297/answer","Biography information for Kit Malthouse","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1105297/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1105297/answer",,,,,"7","Housing, Communities and Local Government","Housing, Communities and Local Government","2019-03-26","Local Plans","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Housing, Communities and Local Government, pursuant to the Answer of 22 February 2019 to Question 220837 on Local Plans, whether his Department has no plans to set a deadline for local authorities to have a local plan.","false","Biography information for Dr Roberta Blackman-Woods","City of Durham","Dr Roberta Blackman-Woods","237085"
