"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1104780","Attorney General","false","2019-03-28","<p>The Attorney General’s Office has not hired any consultants since 2016 to the present time.</p><p> </p>","South Swindon","Robert Buckland",,"2019-03-28T11:05:07.957Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1104780/answer","Biography information for Robert Buckland","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1104780/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1104780/answer",,,,,"88","Attorney General","Attorney General","2019-03-25","Attorney General: Consultants","1","House of Commons","To ask the Attorney General, how many consultants his Department has hired in each year since 2016; and what the cost has been to the public purse.","false","Biography information for Peter Dowd","Bootle","Peter Dowd","236404"
